* 2022年：電影《[[金手指_(2022年電影)|金手指]]》- 程一言 ([[梁朝偉|梁朝偉]] 飾)<ref>{{cite news |author1=王誦賢 |title=金手指︱梁朝偉劉德華18年後再合作　《無間道》黃金組合正式重聚 |url=https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/589343/%E9%87%91%E6%89%8B%E6%8C%87-%E6%A2%81%E6%9C%9D%E5%81%89%E5%8A%89%E5%BE%B7%E8%8F%AF18%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E5%86%8D%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-%E7%84%A1%E9%96%93%E9%81%93-%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E7%B5%84%E5%90%88%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E9%87%8D%E8%81%9A |work=香港01 |date=2021-02-19 |access-date=2022-01-13 |dead-url=no |language=zh-hant}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1= |title=金手指︱劉德華+梁朝偉《無間道》金鑽組合重聚　華仔偉仔18年後再鬥演技 |url=https://topick.hket.com/article/2881530/%E9%87%91%E6%89%8B%E6%8C%87%EF%B8%B1%E5%8A%89%E5%BE%B7%E8%8F%AF-%E6%A2%81%E6%9C%9D%E5%81%89%E3%80%8A%E7%84%A1%E9%96%93%E9%81%93%E3%80%8B%E9%87%91%E9%91%BD%E7%B5%84%E5%90%88%E9%87%8D%E8%81%9A%E3%80%80%E8%8F%AF%E4%BB%94%E5%81%89%E4%BB%9418%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E5%86%8D%E9%AC%A5%E6%BC%94%E6%8A%80 |work=香港經濟日報 |date=2021-02-19 |access-date=2022-01-13 |dead-url=no |language=zh-hant}}</ref>

